SOLUTION TO THE 99.9% PROBLEM:
1. Close the dowloading program (eg. BitComet)
2. Change the .BUP to .VOB.BC! and the files will turn in to unfinished BitComet dowload files.
3. Start your torrent program and the movie will start hashing and after a while you can enjoy the movie:D
This worked on my computer (Win Xp Pro, BitComet) hope it works for you too!
